title: Bianca Buitendag - the African surfer going to Tokyo 2020
description:
South Africa's Bianca Buitendag qualified for the Olympics as surfing makes its first appearance at the Games at Tokyo 2020. Bianca talks about the 'terrifying' world of professional surfing, coming back from family tragedy, and surfing in Japan.

Head to olympicchannel.com/podcast for more than 100 episode featuring surfers like Kelly Slater, Stephanie Gilmore, and Owen Wright.
